snippet.title: Syndicate Deep-Dive: Origins (HD)
snippet.description: Check out the origins of Syndicate, where Business is War and you are the weapon. See how the original Syndicate has been reimagined into a brutal first person shooter of corruption and revenge. Get more news and pre-order at http://Syndicate.EA.com. Follow us on Facebook at http://Facebook.com/Syndicate and Twitter at http://Twitter.com/Syndicate
